ble.'=>'Sebuah aturan firewall telah diaktifkan, tetapi folder /wp-content/ tidak dapat ditulis.','Please set the wp-config.php to writable until the rule has been written.'=>'Silakan setel wp-config.php agar dapat ditulis sampai aturan tersebut selesai ditulis.','A firewall rule was enabled, but the wp-config.php is not writable.'=>'Sebuah aturan firewall telah diaktifkan, tetapi wp-config.php tidak dapat ditulis.','Firewall'=>'Firewall','Visit the plugins overview or %srenew your license%s.'=>'Kunjungi ringkasan plugin atau %sperbarui lisensi Anda%s.','Update Really Simple SSL Pro: the plugin needs to be updated to the latest version to be compatible.'=>'Perbarui Really Simple SSL Pro: plugin butuh pembaruan ke versi terbaru agar sesuai.','Widget with mixed content'=>'Widget dengan konten campuran','Widget area'=>'Area widget','Mixed content in the postmeta table'=>'Konten campuran di tabel postmeta','Mixed content in post: %s'=>'Konten campuran di pos: %s','Mixed content in CSS/JS file from another domain'=>'Konten campuran di file CSS/JS dari domain lain','Copyright warning!'=>'Peringatan hak cipta!','Import and insert file'=>'Impor dan tambahkan berkas','Mixed content in %s'=>'Konten campuran di %s','Details'=>'Detail','Mixed content in PHP file in %s'=>'Konten campuran di file PHP dalam %s','Activate'=>'Aktifkan','Complianz - Consent Management as it should be'=>'Complianz - Manajemen Persetujuan sebagaimana mestinya','Your website\'s ip address is blocked. Please add your domain\'s ip address to the security policy in CPanel'=>'Alamat IP situs Anda diblokir. Mohon tambahkan alamat IP situs Anda ke bagian security policy di CPanel','Renew certificate'=>'Perbarui sertifikat','Renew installation'=>'Perbarui instalasi','Do you want to store these credentials for renewal purposes?'=>'Apakah Anda ingin menyimpan kredensial ini untuk tujuan pembaruan?','Plesk username and password'=>'Nama pengguna dan kata sandi Plesk','Plesk admin URL'=>'URL admin Plesk','CloudWays